  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 947c76105d7454747a8fc8874cd8bff8, type: 3}
  m_Name: Backstory 1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NarrationLines
  lines:
  - My husband, Genji.
  - My sweet, precious Genji.
  - He was the one whom I cherished the most.
  - The one who loved me with all his heart.
  - He was kind, charming, and above all else,
  - 'he was honourable. '
  - His words would soothe every sense of doubt that I had.
  - "It was as though we were made for each other\u2026"
  - "But he had found\u2026"
  line: His words would soothe every sense of doubt that I had.
